  "duaSuhoorTitle": "Intention for Fasting (Suhoor)",
  "duaSuhoorArabic": "نَوَيْتُ أَنْ أَصُومَ صَوْمَ شَهْرِ رَمَضَانَ مِنَ الْفَجْرِ إِلَى الْمَغْرِبِ خَالِصًا لِلَّهِ تَعَالَى",
  "duaSuhoorTranslit": "Nawaytu an asuma sawma shahri ramadana minal fajri ilal maghribi khalisan lillahi ta'ala.",
  "duaSuhoorTransl": "I intend to keep the fast for the month of Ramadan from dawn till dusk sincerely for Allah.",
  "duaIftarTitle": "Dua for Breaking Fast (Iftar)",
  "duaIftarArabic": "اللَّهُمَّ اِنِّى لَكَ صُمْتُ وَبِكَ امَنْتُ وَعَليْكَ تَوَكَّلْتُ وَعَلى رِزْقِكَ اَفْطَرْتُ",
  "duaIftarTranslit": "Allahumma inni laka sumtu wa bika aamantu wa 'alayka tawakkaltu wa 'ala rizqika aftartu.",
  "duaIftarTransl": "O Allah, I fasted for You and I believe in You and I put my trust in You and I break my fast with Your sustenance.",
