  "duaSuhoorTitle": "Dua for Suhoor (Fasting Intention)",
  "duaSuhoorArabic": "نَوَيْتُ أَنْ أَصُومَ صَوْمَ شَهْرِ رَمَضَانَ مِنَ الْفَجْرِ إِلَى الْمَغْرِبِ خَالِصًا لِلَّهِ تَعَالَى",
  "duaSuhoorTrans": "Nawaitu an asuma sawma shahri ramadana minal fajri ilal maghribi khalisan lillahi ta'ala",
  "duaSuhoorTranslate": "I intend to keep the fast for tomorrow in the month of Ramadan, sincerely for Allah.",

  "duaIftarTitle": "Dua for Iftar (Breaking Fast)",
  "duaIftarArabic": "ذَهَبَ الظَّمَأُ وَابْتَلَّتِ الْعُرُوقُ وَثَبَتَ الْأَجْرُ إِنْ شَاءَ اللَّهُ",
  "duaIftarTrans": "Dhahabadh-dhama'u wabtallatil-'urooqu wa thabatal-ajru in sha'Allah",
  "duaIftarTranslate": "The thirst has gone, the veins are quenched, and the reward is confirmed, if Allah wills.",

  "dua_qadr_title": "Dua for Laylat al-Qadr",
  "dua_qadr_ar": "اللَّهُمَّ إِنَّكَ عَفُوٌّ تُحِبُّ الْعَفْوَ فَاعْفُ عَنِّي",
  "dua_qadr_trans": "Allahumma innaka 'afuwwun tuhibbul-'afwa fa'fu 'anni",
  "dua_qadr_text": "O Allah, You are Forgiving and love forgiveness, so forgive me.",

  "dua_kursi_title": "Ayat al-Kursi",
  "dua_kursi_ar": "اللَّهُ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا هُوَ الْحَيُّ الْقَيُّومُ لَا تَأْخُذُهُ سِنَةٌ وَلَا نَوْمٌ لَّهُ مَا فِي السَّمَاوَاتِ وَمَا فِي الْأَرْضِ مَن ذَا الَّذِي يَشْفَعُ عِندَهُ إِلَّا بِإِذْنِهِ يَعْلَمُ مَا بَيْنَ أَيْدِيهِمْ وَمَا خَلْفَهُمْ وَلَا يُحِيطُونَ بِشَيْءٍ مِّنْ عِلْمِهِ إِلَّا بِمَا شَاءَ وَسِعَ كُرْسِيُّهُ السَّمَاوَاتِ وَالْأَرْضَ وَلَا يَئُودُهُ حِفْظُهُمَا وَهُوَ الْعَلِيُّ الْعَظِيمُ",
  "dua_kursi_trans": "Allahu la ilaha illa Huwal-Hayyul-Qayyum. La ta'khudhuhu sinatun wa la nawm...",
  "dua_kursi_text": "Allah! There is no deity except Him, the Ever-Living, the Sustainer of [all] existence. Neither drowsiness overtakes Him nor sleep...",

  "dua_istighfar_title": "Sayyidul Istighfar",
  "dua_istighfar_ar": "اللَّهُمَّ أَنْتَ رَبِّي لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا أَنْتَ خَلَقْتَنِي وَأَنَا عَبْدُكَ وَأَنَا عَلَى عَهْدِكَ وَوَعْدِكَ مَا اسْتَطَعْتُ أَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنْ شَرِّ مَا صَنَعْتُ أَبُوءُ لَكَ بِنِعْمَتِكَ عَلَيَّ وَأَبُوءُ بِذَنْبِي فَاغْفِرْ لِي فَإِنَّهُ لَا يَغْفِرُ الذُّنُوبَ إِلَّا أَنْتَ",
  "dua_istighfar_trans": "Allahumma Anta Rabbi la ilaha illa Anta, khalaqtani wa ana 'abduka...",
  "dua_istighfar_text": "O Allah, You are my Lord, there is no deity except You. You created me and I am Your servant...",

  "dua_sadness_title": "Dua for Anxiety and Sorrow",
  "dua_sadness_ar": "اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنَ الْهَمِّ وَالْحَزَنِ",
  "dua_sadness_trans": "Allahumma inni a'udhu bika minal-hammi wal-hazan",
  "dua_sadness_text": "O Allah, I seek refuge in You from anxiety and sorrow.",

  "dua_morning_title": "Protection for the Day",
  "dua_morning_ar": "بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الَّذِي لَا يَضُرُّ مَعَ اسْمِهِ شَيْءٌ فِي الْأَرْضِ وَلَا فِي السَّمَاءِ وَهُوَ السَّمِيعُ الْعَلِيمُ",
  "dua_morning_trans": "Bismillahil-ladhi la yadurru ma'asmihi shay'un fil-ardi wa la fis-sama'i wa huwas-Sami'ul-'Alim",
  "dua_morning_text": "In the name of Allah, with Whose name nothing can cause harm in the earth nor in the heavens, and He is the All-Hearing, the All-Knowing."
}